verbose_text: RT-qPCR assays for SARS-CoV-2 were performed in 25-muL qPCR reaction volume containing 12.5 muL of Probe qPCR Mix with UNG (Takara Bio, Kusatsu, Japan), 0.1 muL each of 100 muM forward and reverse primers, 0.05 muL of 100 muM TaqMan probe, and 2.5 muL of template cDNA.
